posts.subject: A little help?
posts.body:

What could this possibly mean? I just want to get my own comfy chan started (with credit given to this one, of course.). Any help resolving this issue is appreciated.

rip this board... and honestly... this site.

You're too stupid to understand that samefagging is bad.

This board was made due to the fact that this site, with as much potential that is has, has been flooded to the absolute brim with horny 60 year old boomers who do nothing but post and circlejerk over sub-par, not-very-attractive e-thots/pornstars 24/7 (Essentially modern 4chan's /b/).

Not really sure what the board rules should be, except for, obviously, No fucking boomerposting, or hornyposting (except if it's anime tiddies).

Enjoy.
